abstract.text: The optimized representation of a compute graph of operations and tensors.

inlineContent.text: An MPSGraph is a symbolic representation of operations to be utilized to execute compute graphs on a device.

abstract.text: Build, compile, and execute compute graphs utilizing all the different compute devices on the platform, including GPU, CPU, and Neural Engine.
